data.title: Artie Lange's Beer League Ed's Bar And Swill Worn Look Raglan T Shirt
data.meta_description: • Available in multiple colors, premium t-shirts, ladies t-shirts, hoodies, crewneck sweatshirts, baseball raglans, tank tops, iPhone cases and more• $4.95 flat rate US shipping on tees• Made in North AmericaAll prints are on the front of the apparel unless otherwise stated. For back prints leave a comment in the purchasing notes or email us at cocoateeinfo@gmail.comReturn policyTerms and conditions apply
data.text:
Do you accept returns or exchanges?

All sales are final and we do not accept returns or exchanges for change of heart or choosing the wrong size or model. In the rare instance that you are sent the wrong order, there are mistakes with your delivered order (defects or sent the wrong size) or you order was undeliverable or lost (verified via tracking information provided), we will give you, the buyer, the option of a replacement order or a refund. See below for more details.

Please find sizing info here.

What if my order has a mistake or defect?

If you receive the wrong item, wrong size or an item with a defect please contact us immediately. We will make every attempt to rectify any mistakes on our part in a timely manner. In most instances this means sending a replacement order or providing a refund. Please note that defects or mistakes should be reported within 30 days.

My order is missing what should I do?

If your order is missing, not deliverable or showing it is stuck in the postal system, please contact us as soon as possible. We will contact the courier and attempt to get your order out to you. In most situations this resolves the problem but if it doesn’t we will gladly re-send your order or offer a full refund.

When ordering for a special occasion please allow sufficient time for delivery. When the order is handed over to the courier we can't account for delays within the postal system.
